<p class="ayah 15-28" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ رَبُّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to the Angels,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Indeed, I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِقُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) create</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَشَرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a human being</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(out) of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَلْصَـٰلٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">clay</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَمَإٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">black mud</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّسْنُونٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">altered.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/15:28" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1830"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>28<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 15-29" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So, when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَوَّيْتُهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I have fashioned him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنَفَخْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and [I] breathed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">into him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رُّوحِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">My spirit,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقَعُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then fall down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَـٰجِدِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">prostrating."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/15:29" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1831"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>29<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
