<p class="ayah 15-40" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Except,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِبَادَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Your slaves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُخْلَصِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the ones who are sincere."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/15:40" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1842"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>40<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
